  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sound Management of Unintentional Persistent Organic Pollutants (POPs) and Polychlorinated Biphenyl Ether (PBDEs) to Reduce their Emission from the Industrial Waste Sector</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The objective of this project is to establish the sound management system of unintentional POPs (uPOPs) and polybrominated diphenyl ethers (PBDEs) and final disposal of possibly PBDE-contaminated Waste of Electrical and Electronic Equiment (WEEE) and End of Life Vehicles (ELV).</narrative>
